    uniqueIntro: 'Ceiling fan installations are a popular home comfort upgrade throughout Encinitas — from indoor living areas in Leucadia and Cardiff to covered patios in Olivenhain and Encinitas Ranch. Wheyland Electric installs fans correctly with fan-rated boxes, proper wiring, and full speed and light kit testing.',
